    {
      "id": "5b1b9d4f-8b22-4a2b-9b7c-1d3d2e5a6f88",
      "title": "CIA Triad — Practical Mapping",
      "category": "security",
      "body_markdown": "Confidentiality → Encryption (TLS, AES).\n\nIntegrity → Hashing/Signing (SHA-256, HMAC).\n\nAvailability → Redundancy and failover (clusters, backups).",
      "code_blocks": [
        {
          "lang": "text",
          "content": "TLS: encryption + key exchange\nHMAC: integrity + authenticity\nDR: backups + failover"
        }
      ],
