      "id": "c3a0e7b2-6a4f-4c2a-8d7c-44d5b7a1c0de",
      "title": "Netmiko — SSH Device Automation",
      "category": "python",
      "body_markdown": "Use ConnectHandler to SSH into Cisco IOS.\n\nAlways disconnect() after running commands.\n\nPrefer collecting output and parsing after the session ends.",
      "code_blocks": [
        {
          "lang": "python",
          "content": "from netmiko import ConnectHandler\n\nconn = ConnectHandler(device_type='cisco_ios', host='10.0.0.1', username='u', password='p')\noutput = conn.send_command('show ip ospf neighbor')\nconn.disconnect()"
        }
      ],
