    {
      "id": "a1d2c3e4-f5a6-4b7c-8d9e-0f1a2b3c4d5e",
      "title": "STP Port States & Root Election",
      "category": "switching",
      "body_markdown": "Root bridge = lowest Bridge ID (priority + MAC).\n\nPort states: Blocking → Listening → Learning → Forwarding.\n\nConvergence depends on timer configuration and topology changes.",
      "code_blocks": [
        {
          "lang": "text",
          "content": "Debug goal: identify root changes and port transitions\nVerify: show spanning-tree root\nVerify: show spanning-tree interface <port>"
        }
      ],
