    {
      "id": "f2c4d6e8-1a2b-4c3d-9e8f-7a6b5c4d3e2f",
      "title": "BGP Path Selection — 12 Attributes",
      "category": "bgp",
      "body_markdown": "Weight → Local Pref → Originate → AS-PATH → Origin → MED → eBGP over iBGP → IGP metric → oldest → RID → neighbor IP.\n\nPractical takeaway: attributes order defines the decision path.",
      "code_blocks": [
        {
          "lang": "text",
          "content": "neighbor 10.0.0.1 weight 200"
        }
      ],
