      "title": "IPsec VPN — IKE Phase 1 & 2",
      "category": "security",
      "body_markdown": "Phase 1 establishes ISAKMP SA (auth, DH group).\n\nPhase 2 negotiates IPsec SA (ESP/AH, encryption).\n\nQuick mode builds the tunnel configuration.",
      "code_blocks": [
        {
          "lang": "text",
          "content": "IKEv1:\n- Phase 1: ISAKMP SA\n- Phase 2: IPsec SA (transform sets)"
        }
      ],
